Installation Guide

1. Clone the repository

   git clone https://github.com/Regista6/EA-FC-Squad-Builder.git
   cd EA-FC-Squad-Builder

2. Create a virtual environment

   python -m venv venv
   .\venv\Scripts\activate       # On Windows

3. Install required dependencies

   pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Configure your input data

   * Open `input.py` and customize SBC constraints (e.g. league, nationality, chemistry).
   * Optionally, modify `main.py` to point to your specific player/club dataset (if different from the default).

5. Run the code

   python main.py

6. Get the result

   * The optimal squad will be saved to `output.xlsx`.
